# SPA fallback for Cloudflare Pages. With web.output "single" the app is one
# index.html hydrated client-side; serve it for any path so deep links and
# refreshes on routes like /sign-in resolve instead of 404ing.
#
# EXCEPTION (must stay first): /privacy serves the static, crawlable privacy.html, not the
# SPA shell, so a non-JS crawler (Google Play's policy check) gets the real policy text.
/privacy    /privacy.html   200
/*    /index.html   200
